---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Free Ecommerce Growth Review" description="Share your ecommerce growth context and receive a practical opportunity map across acquisition, conversion, retention and measurement.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs-wrap"><Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Growth review' }]} /></div>
  <section class="contact-hero hero-dark">
    <div class="container contact-hero-grid">
      <div><span class="badge">Free ecommerce growth review</span><h1>Find the next constraint worth removing.</h1><p>Share the commercial context behind your store. We will review the customer journey and return a concise opportunity map with priorities, quick wins and the questions that need deeper evidence.</p></div>
      <div class="audit-preview">
        <span>What you receive</span>
        <ol>
          <li><div><strong>Commercial snapshot</strong><small>Targets, economics and current channel mix</small></div></li>
          <li><div><strong>Constraint map</strong><small>Acquire, convert, retain and measure</small></div></li>
          <li><div><strong>Prioritised next steps</strong><small>Impact, confidence and dependencies</small></div></li>
        </ol>
        <p>No obligation. Useful even if we do not work together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section surface">
    <div class="container contact-layout">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Tell us about the store</span>
        <h2>A little context makes the review much more useful.</h2>
        <p class="form-intro">Required fields are deliberately limited. Commercial ranges help us tailor the review but are optional.</p>
        <div class="journey-context" id="journey-context" hidden role="status"><span>Journey context retained</span><strong id="journey-context-label"></strong><p>We will include the page and topic that brought you here with the enquiry.</p></div>
        <div class="shared-result" id="shared-result" hidden>
          <span>Result ready to share</span>
          <strong id="shared-result-title"></strong>
          <pre id="shared-result-preview"></pre>
          <p>Nothing is added to the form until you choose to include it. Review and edit the summary before sending.</p>
          <div><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="add-shared-result">Add result to my message</button><button type="button" class="discard-result" id="discard-shared-result">Discard</button></div>
          <p class="shared-result-status" id="shared-result-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
        </div>
        <form class="growth-form form-stack" action="https://formsubmit.co/jack@spiresdigital.com" method="POST" data-capture-attribution data-growth-form>
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New ecommerce growth review request" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://spiresdigital.com/thank-you/" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" class="honey" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Leave this field blank" aria-hidden="true" />
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field"><label for="name">Your name *</label><input id="name" name="name" autocomplete="name" required /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="email">Work email *</label><input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field"><label for="company">Brand / company *</label><input id="company" name="company" autocomplete="organization" required /></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="website">Store URL *</label><input id="website" name="website" type="url" inputmode="url" placeholder="https://" required /></div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field"><label for="platform">Ecommerce platform</label><select id="platform" name="platform"><option value="">Select platform</option><option>Shopify</option><option>WooCommerce</option><option>BigCommerce</option><option>Magento / Adobe Commerce</option><option>Custom platform</option><option>Other / unsure</option></select></div>
            <div class="field"><label for="revenue">Approximate annual online revenue</label><select id="revenue" name="annual_revenue"><option value="">Prefer not to say</option><option>Pre-revenue / launching</option><option>Under £100k</option><option>£100k–£500k</option><option>£500k–£1m</option><option>£1m–£5m</option><option>£5m+</option></select></div>
          </div>
          <fieldset class="challenge-field"><legend>Where does growth feel most constrained?</legend><div class="choice-grid"><label><input type="checkbox" name="constraint" value="Acquisition" /><span><strong>Acquire</strong><small>Paid, SEO or affiliate growth</small></span></label><label><input type="checkbox" name="constraint" value="Conversion" /><span><strong>Convert</strong><small>Store and checkout performance</small></span></label><label><input type="checkbox" name="constraint" value="Retention" /><span><strong>Retain</strong><small>Email and repeat purchase</small></span></label><label><input type="checkbox" name="constraint" value="Measurement" /><span><strong>Measure</strong><small>Tracking and profit clarity</small></span></label></div></fieldset>
          <div class="field"><label for="context">What are you trying to improve? *</label><textarea id="context" name="context" rows="5" placeholder="A useful answer might include your target, what has already been tried, and the result you are seeing now." required></textarea><span class="field-hint">Please do not include account passwords or other sensitive access details.</span></div>
          <div class="consent-row"><label><input type="checkbox" name="privacy_acknowledged" required /> <span>I agree that Spires Digital can use this information to respond to my request. *</span></label><a href="/privacy">Privacy policy</a></div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-arrow">Request my growth review</button>
          <p class="submit-note">We aim to reply within one working day. Your details are not added to a marketing list.</p>
          <div class="delivery-fallback" id="delivery-fallback" hidden role="status"><strong>The form has not moved on yet.</strong><p>You can try again or <a href="mailto:jack@spiresdigital.com?subject=Ecommerce%20growth%20review">email Jack directly</a>. Your typed answers remain on this page.</p></div>
          <noscript><p class="delivery-fallback"><strong>JavaScript is off.</strong> The form still works, or you can email <a href="mailto:jack@spiresdigital.com?subject=Ecommerce%20growth%20review">jack@spiresdigital.com</a>.</p></noscript>
        </form>
      </div>
      <aside class="contact-side">
        <div class="direct-card"><span>Consultation-first pricing</span><h3>Book 30 minutes with Jack.</h3><p>We need to understand your goals, current setup and delivery requirements before giving a price. If there is a strong fit, the consultation is followed by a clear written scope and quote—with no obligation to proceed.</p><a href="https://calendly.com/jack-spiresdigital/30min?back=1" class="btn btn-secondary btn-arrow" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-track="contact_calendly">Book a pricing consultation</a></div>
        <div class="fit-card"><span>A strong fit</span><ul class="check-list"><li>Ecommerce is a meaningful part of your revenue</li><li>You want profit clarity across channels</li><li>You value account ownership and transparency</li><li>You can implement or collaborate on recommendations</li></ul></div>
        <div class="direct-links"><a href="mailto:jack@spiresdigital.com" data-track="contact_email"><span>Email directly</span><strong>jack@spiresdigital.com</strong></a><div><span>Based in</span><strong>Guernsey, Channel Islands</strong></div></div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const growthForm = document.querySelector('[data-growth-form]');
  const journeyParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
  const interest = journeyParams.get('interest') || '';
  const sourcePage = journeyParams.get('source_page') || '/';
  const interestLabels = {
    'service:ppc-management': 'Google Shopping & PPC',
    'service:meta-ads': 'Meta advertising',
    'service:ecommerce-seo': 'Ecommerce SEO',
    'service:affiliate-management': 'Affiliate growth',
    'service:cro-shopify': 'CRO & Shopify',
    'service:email-retention': 'Email & retention',
    'service:analytics-attribution': 'Analytics & attribution',
    'tool:ecommerce-profit-calculator': 'Profit & break-even ROAS calculator',
    'tool:channel-budget-planner': 'Channel budget planner',
    'tool:growth-assessment': 'Store growth assessment',
    'tool:google-ads-audit-checklist': 'Ecommerce Google Ads audit checklist',
    'tool:google-ads-vat-guide': 'Google Ads VAT guide',
    'tool:paid-media-waste-estimator': 'Paid-media waste estimator',
    'tool:keyword-density-checker': 'Keyword density & content analyser',
    'industry:ecommerce': 'Ecommerce growth',
  };
  const constraintByInterest = {
    'service:ppc-management': 'Acquisition',
    'service:meta-ads': 'Acquisition',
    'service:ecommerce-seo': 'Acquisition',
    'service:affiliate-management': 'Acquisition',
    'service:cro-shopify': 'Conversion',
    'service:email-retention': 'Retention',
    'service:analytics-attribution': 'Measurement',
    'tool:ecommerce-profit-calculator': 'Measurement',
    'tool:channel-budget-planner': 'Acquisition',
    'tool:growth-assessment': 'Measurement',
    'tool:google-ads-audit-checklist': 'Acquisition',
    'tool:google-ads-vat-guide': 'Measurement',
    'tool:paid-media-waste-estimator': 'Acquisition',
    'tool:keyword-density-checker': 'Acquisition',
  };
  const contextLabel = interestLabels[interest] || (sourcePage !== '/' ? sourcePage : 'Your current website journey');
  if (interest || sourcePage !== '/') {
    const contextPanel = document.getElementById('journey-context');
    document.getElementById('journey-context-label').textContent = contextLabel;
    contextPanel.hidden = false;
  }
  const suggestedConstraint = constraintByInterest[interest];
  if (suggestedConstraint) growthForm?.querySelector(`input[name="constraint"][value="${suggestedConstraint}"]`)?.click();

  if (journeyParams.get('share_result') === '1') {
    try {
      const shared = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem('spires_shared_tool_result') || 'null');
      const isRecent = Number(shared?.createdAt) > Date.now() - (2 * 60 * 60 * 1000);
      const summary = String(shared?.summary || '').trim().slice(0, 3000);
      if (shared && isRecent && summary) {
        const panel = document.getElementById('shared-result');
        document.getElementById('shared-result-title').textContent = String(shared.title || 'Tool result');
        document.getElementById('shared-result-preview').textContent = summary;
        panel.hidden = false;
        const addSharedButton = document.getElementById('add-shared-result');
        addSharedButton?.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const context = document.getElementById('context');
          const existing = context.value.trim();
          context.value = `${existing}${existing ? '\n\n' : ''}Tool result I would like to discuss:\n\n${summary}`;
          context.focus();
          addSharedButton.disabled = true;
          addSharedButton.textContent = 'Result added';
          document.getElementById('shared-result-status').textContent = 'Result added. You can edit it before sending.';
          sessionStorage.removeItem('spires_shared_tool_result');
        });
        document.getElementById('discard-shared-result')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
          sessionStorage.removeItem('spires_shared_tool_result');
          panel.hidden = true;
        });
      }
    } catch { /* A consultation can still be requested without the stored summary. */ }
  }

  growthForm?.addEventListener('submit', event => {
    if (['localhost', '127.0.0.1'].includes(window.location.hostname)) event.preventDefault();
    const data = new FormData(growthForm);
    const constraints = data.getAll('constraint').map(String);
    const contextLength = String(data.get('context') || '').trim().length;
    const completenessPoints = Number(Boolean(data.get('platform'))) + Number(Boolean(data.get('annual_revenue'))) + Number(constraints.length > 0) + Number(contextLength >= 120);
    const contextCompleteness = completenessPoints >= 3 ? 'detailed' : completenessPoints >= 1 ? 'useful' : 'basic';
    const addHidden = (name, value) => {
      let input = growthForm.querySelector(`input[name="${name}"]`);
      if (!input) { input = document.createElement('input'); input.type = 'hidden'; input.name = name; growthForm.appendChild(input); }
      input.value = value;
    };
    addHidden('constraint_summary', constraints.join(', ') || 'Not selected');
    addHidden('context_completeness', contextCompleteness);

    const leadContext = {
      lead_type: 'growth_review',
      source_page: String(data.get('source_page') || sourcePage).slice(0, 180),
      landing_page: String(data.get('landing_page') || sourcePage).slice(0, 180),
      lead_interest: String(data.get('lead_interest') || interest || 'general').slice(0, 100),
      acquisition_source: String(data.get('acquisition_source') || 'direct').slice(0, 100),
      constraint_group: constraints.join('|') || 'not_selected',
      platform: String(data.get('platform') || 'not_selected').slice(0, 50),
      revenue_band: String(data.get('annual_revenue') || 'not_selected').slice(0, 50),
      context_completeness: contextCompleteness,
    };
    try { sessionStorage.setItem('spires_pending_lead', JSON.stringify(leadContext)); } catch { /* Form delivery is not dependent on storage. */ }
    window.trackSpiresEvent?.('lead_submit_attempt', leadContext);

    const submitButton = growthForm.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
    submitButton.disabled = true;
    submitButton.textContent = 'Sending your request…';
    window.setTimeout(() => {
      submitButton.disabled = false;
      submitButton.textContent = 'Request my growth review';
      document.getElementById('delivery-fallback').hidden = false;
    }, 8000);
  });
</script>

<style>
  .contact-hero { padding-top: 5rem; }
  .contact-hero-grid { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .75fr; gap: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 6rem); align-items: center; }
  .audit-preview { padding: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15); border-radius: var(--radius); background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); }
  .audit-preview > span { color: #91eadb; font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .audit-preview ol { display: grid; gap: .7rem; margin: 1.2rem 0; list-style: none; counter-reset: review; }
  .audit-preview li { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 32px minmax(0, 1fr); gap: .8rem; align-items: start; counter-increment: review; }
  .audit-preview li::before { display: grid; width: 32px; height: 32px; place-items: center; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(117,230,211,.12); color: #91eadb; content: counter(review); font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 800; }
  .audit-preview li > div { min-width: 0; padding-top: .05rem; }
  .audit-preview strong, .audit-preview small { display: block; }.audit-preview strong { color: white; line-height: 1.3; }.audit-preview small { margin-top: .18rem; color: #9da8ba; line-height: 1.45; }
  .audit-preview > p { margin: 0; color: #cbd2df; font-size: .75rem; }
  .contact-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(300px, .65fr); gap: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 6rem); align-items: start; }
  .contact-layout h2 { max-width: 760px; }
  .form-intro { margin: 1rem 0 2rem; color: var(--slate); }
  .journey-context { margin: 0 0 1.2rem; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #cce9e2; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: #effbf8; }
  .journey-context span, .journey-context strong { display: block; }.journey-context span { color: var(--success); font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }.journey-context strong { margin-top: .25rem; color: var(--ink); }.journey-context p { margin-top: .2rem; color: var(--slate); font-size: .72rem; }
  .shared-result { margin: 0 0 1.2rem; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #cce9e2; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); background: #effbf8; }.shared-result > span,.shared-result > strong { display: block; }.shared-result > span { color: var(--success); font-size: .65rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }.shared-result > strong { margin-top: .25rem; color: var(--ink); }.shared-result pre { max-height: 220px; margin: .8rem 0; padding: .8rem; overflow: auto; border: 1px solid #dfeeea; border-radius: 8px; background: white; color: var(--slate); font: inherit; font-size: .7rem; white-space: pre-wrap; }.shared-result > p { color: var(--slate); font-size: .7rem; }.shared-result > div { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .6rem; margin-top: .8rem; }.shared-result .btn { padding: .65rem .8rem; }.discard-result { border: 0; background: transparent; color: var(--violet-dark); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: underline; }.shared-result .shared-result-status { min-height: 1em; margin-top: .55rem; color: var(--success); font-weight: 700; }
  .growth-form { padding: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2rem); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); background: var(--canvas); }
  .honey { position: absolute !important; left: -9999px !important; }
  .challenge-field { border: 0; }.challenge-field legend { margin-bottom: .55rem; color: var(--ink); font-size: .84rem; font-weight: 750; }
  .choice-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: .6rem; }
  .choice-grid label { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: .65rem; align-items: start; padding: .8rem; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 9px; background: white; cursor: pointer; }
  .choice-grid input { margin-top: .22rem; accent-color: var(--violet); }
  .choice-grid strong, .choice-grid small { display: block; }.choice-grid small { color: var(--muted); }
  .consent-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; align-items: start; color: var(--slate); font-size: .75rem; }
  .consent-row label { display: flex; gap: .5rem; }.consent-row input { margin-top: .25rem; accent-color: var(--violet); }.consent-row a { color: var(--violet-dark); text-decoration: underline; white-space: nowrap; }
  .submit-note { color: var(--muted); font-size: .72rem; text-align: center; }
  .delivery-fallback { padding: .9rem; border: 1px solid #f0d8aa; border-radius: 9px; background: #fff8eb; color: #765629; font-size: .74rem; }.delivery-fallback p { margin-top: .2rem; }.delivery-fallback a { color: var(--violet-dark); font-weight: 800; text-decoration: underline; }
  .contact-side { position: sticky; top: 110px; display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
  .direct-card, .fit-card, .direct-links { padding: 1.4rem; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); background: white; }
  .direct-card > span, .fit-card > span { color: var(--violet-dark); font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .direct-card h3 { margin: 1rem 0 .7rem; }.direct-card p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--slate); font-size: .84rem; }.direct-card .btn { width: 100%; }
  .fit-card .check-list { margin-top: 1rem; font-size: .8rem; }
  .direct-links { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }.direct-links a, .direct-links div { display: grid; }.direct-links span { color: var(--muted); font-size: .68rem; }.direct-links strong { color: var(--ink); font-size: .84rem; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .contact-hero-grid, .contact-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .contact-side { position: static; } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .choice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .consent-row { flex-direction: column; } }
</style>
